longer (inflection of dug)
cesta A je dulja od ceste B - road A is longer than road B;
danas su dani dulji nego prošlog mjeseca - today's days are longer than last month.

longer (inflection of dug)
cesta A je duža od ceste B - road A is longer than road B;
danas su dani duži nego prošlog mjeseca - today's days are longer than last month.
